@startuml
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "API Layer" as API
participant "Authentication" as Auth
participant "Board Service" as BoardSvc
participant "Note Service" as NoteSvc
participant "WebSocket" as WS
participant "Database" as DB
participant "NATS/Redis" as NR

FE -> API: User logs in
API -> Auth: Authenticate user
Auth --> API: Authentication result
API --> FE: Login response

FE -> API: Create new board
API -> BoardSvc: Create board
BoardSvc -> DB: Save board
DB --> BoardSvc: Board created
BoardSvc --> API: Board details
API --> FE: Board creation response

FE -> WS: Connect to board
WS -> BoardSvc: Register user to board
BoardSvc -> NR: Publish user joined event
NR --> FE: Broadcast user joined

FE -> API: Add note to board
API -> NoteSvc: Create note
NoteSvc -> DB: Save note
DB --> NoteSvc: Note saved
NoteSvc -> NR: Publish note added event
NR --> FE: Broadcast note added

FE -> API: Vote on note
API -> NoteSvc: Update note votes
NoteSvc -> DB: Save updated note
DB --> NoteSvc: Note updated
NoteSvc -> NR: Publish vote update event
NR --> FE: Broadcast vote update

FE -> API: Export board data
API -> BoardSvc: Get board data
BoardSvc -> DB: Retrieve board and notes
DB --> BoardSvc: Board data
BoardSvc --> API: Formatted board data
API --> FE: Board export file

FE -> WS: Disconnect from board
WS -> BoardSvc: Unregister user from board
BoardSvc -> NR: Publish user left event
NR --> FE: Broadcast user left
@enduml